Jeramy HOLLINGSHEAD, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
DC MISFITS, LLC, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-1225 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION
